{"tid":193630,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"6月廣島四國行程求救","createTime":"2017-04-09T12:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-11T15:49:34.000Z","uid":12320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"66743543f0276b899388ba87d3e6ea640e7e6698","tid":193630,"uid":12320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T12:15:36.000Z","msg":"黎緊6月諗住去兩個禮拜廣島同四國，第一次一個人獨遊日本，麻煩巴絲打幫我睇下行程<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\nDay1:香港-&gt;廣島<br />\nDay2:宮島<br />\nDay3:兔島+尾道<br />\nDay4:廣島市中心+岩國<br />\nDay5:山口<br />\nDay6:美禰<br />\nDay7:岡山<br />\nDay8:高松<br />\nDay9:小豆島<br />\nDay10:琴平+德島<br />\nDay11:祖谷<br />\nDay12:鳴門+德島<br />\nDay13:高松<br />\nDay14:高松-&gt;香港<br />\n<br />\n諗住Day2開始用7日山陽山陰周遊券，啱啱好用到Day8去埋高松，之後再買四國既jr pass，唔知咁樣用pass抵唔抵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db867a3f78231a0acb87022861d8e6ecb2acfa09","tid":193630,"uid":12320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T13:08:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f606ece9daeff977ac94b9f177f38024ec18c70b","tid":193630,"uid":26969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T18:38:50.000Z","msg":"我6月都去廣島四國9日 都係廣島去高松走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫你up up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"faca185a7cdbf9aecbac999b232575f59615228e","tid":193630,"uid":19310,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-09T22:31:43.000Z","msg":"1. 宮島同岩國比較近<br />\n2. 德島同琴平係唔順路, 點都要轉車<br />\n3. 高松係好悶"},{"pid":"de315413e6b75883f62587f3c5b43fa8cac41741","tid":193630,"uid":12320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:18:56.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>1. 宮島同岩國比較近<br />\n2. 德島同琴平係唔順路, 點都要轉車<br />\n3. 高松係好悶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 一日玩唔玩得晒宮島同岩國？因為我想睇晒潮漲潮退<br />\n2. 因為果晚會係德島訓，所以諗住去完琴平就即刻去德島<br />\n3.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a34bbf734ac75f75848dcc0dc731427614725cd","tid":193630,"uid":12320,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T01:19:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我6月都去廣島四國9日 都係廣島去高松走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n幫你up up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n可唔可以借你個行程參考下？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d172960cb66dd1658a8dd287dbc6e3cfc202777f","tid":193630,"uid":47637,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:01:17.000Z","msg":"5月廣島入 大阪走<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a6233375d897d8d98393f3fa3985f8507e2d4ee","tid":193630,"uid":39816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-10T02:37:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>1. 宮島同岩國比較近<br />\n2. 德島同琴平係唔順路, 點都要轉車<br />\n3. 高松係好悶</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 一日玩唔玩得晒宮島同岩國？因為我想睇晒潮漲潮退<br />\n2. 因為果晚會係德島訓，所以諗住去完琴平就即刻去德島<br />\n3.<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n1. 如果要睇晒潮漲潮退你要留意下你去個日既潮汐時間.<br />\n潮汐表<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.miyajima.or.jp/sio/sio06.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.miyajima.or.jp%2Fsio%2Fsio06.html&d=KoefzaQlkmro%2FPgOzv92F9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=9d4c8b7d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.miyajima.or.jp/sio/sio06.html</a> &lt;&lt; 今日入唔到去<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.haichaobiao.com/jp/hiroshima/itsukushima\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.haichaobiao.com%2Fjp%2F